      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Al Husayn Bin Muhammad, from Moalla Bin Muhammad, from Al Hassan Bin Ali, from Aban Bin Usman, from Al Fazl Abu Al Abbas, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> regarding <span class=\"ibTxt\"><a href=\"/#/books/quran:2#h196\"><a href=\"/books/quran:2#h196\">[2:196]</a></a> And complete the Hajj and the Umrah for Allah</span>. He<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘Both are necessities’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "2. AI-Husayn ibn Muhammad has narrated, from Mu‘afla’ ibn Muhammad, from al-Hassan ibn Ali, from Aban ibn ‘Uthman from al- Fadl abu af-‘Abbas who has said the following: “About the words of Allah: ‘Complete al-Hajj and al-‘Umrah for the sake of Allah’ <a href=\"/#/books/quran:2#h196\"><a href=\"/books/quran:2#h196\">[2:196]</a></a> abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said that they are obligatory.” "
        ]
      }
